videos.description: Deangelo Antoine would break several tackles and on a 20-yard burst resulting in a field goal for the Bulls to give them the early over the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Antonie run gets Bulls closer to FG

videos.description: Darius Tice pads South Florida's lead with an 11-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Tice scores first TD of the night

videos.description: Hayden Moore's pass is picked off by Bull's Auggie Sanchez and returned for a 65-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: South Florida closes quarter with pick-6

videos.description: With Quinton Flowers' 1-yard touchdown, South Florida has its 23rd game scoring 30 points or more.
videos.headline: Flowers TD extends Bulls scoring streak

videos.description: Cincinnati quarterback Hayden Moore is sacked by Juwuan Brown who forces the fumble and recovers for South Florida.
videos.headline: Bulls force turnover

videos.description: After a slow start, Quinton Flowers propels his team to yet another victory to remain undefeated so far this season.
videos.headline: Breaking down South Florida's victory over Cincinnati
